stories.text:
Hi everyone! Scratched an itch and solved an issue I had while trying to stay up to date with crypto and blockchain news. I realized I was spending too much time bouncing around various sites to find recent news articles. So I built https://blokfeed.com to help me sift through crypto news more efficiently. I have plans on building in more features.

Check it out - hope it helps you as well! blokfeed.com
